{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.13\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">大卫的诗。交给圣咏团长。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">求耶和华看顾</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>耶和华啊，你忘记我要到几时呢？要到永远吗？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">你转脸不顾我要到几时呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>我心里筹算，终日愁苦，要到几时呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">我的仇敌升高压制我，要到几时呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>耶和华－我的上帝啊，求你看顾我，应允我！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">求你使我眼目明亮，免得我沉睡至死；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>免得我的仇敌说“我胜了他”；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">免得我的敌人在我动摇的时候喜乐。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>但我倚靠你的慈爱，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">我的心因你的救恩快乐。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>我要向耶和华歌唱，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">因他厚厚地恩待我。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}